{"tid":26003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌柒到我以後唔敢搭地鐵","createTime":"2016-12-06T12:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T16:04:01.000Z","uid":13771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32f43279d56da0eefb19380d4a4bb9a608d405ec","tid":26003,"uid":13771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"果陣我係放學時間搭<br />\n所以地鐵入面都幾多人<br />\n跟住我就迫左入去車廂最入面<br />\n成個人挨住個門口位<br />\n搭左幾站一直都係對面落<br />\n點知有一站係我挨緊果邊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔知道on99咁繼續挨<br />\n結果一開門 我成個人失重心<br />\n退後左一步就成個人跌左落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家我仲未忘記到周圍既人既忍笑樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd2fc82c113bd6d8c7d2ec1aed31b4328ec8cab","tid":26003,"uid":3838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"巴打定絲打<br />\n絲打就應該冇咩野既"},{"pid":"1e7802ab4781b21b68ac89932fbc70c2302333b3","tid":26003,"uid":13771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打定絲打<br />\n絲打就應該冇咩野既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲 但係巴定絲都係柒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efcc8666b78278d5531db5a4e0326c2c375458e","tid":26003,"uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"我之前試過戴headphone低住頭上車<br />\n閂門嗰時夾甩咗個headphone<br />\n柒到下站即落"},{"pid":"de1aac5dfaf52aafddb2631de25024f197fdde52","tid":26003,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2a675cd648c21f8db9c7396bfc90aa91e9d7c63","tid":26003,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"等我保護你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817f27bd4d4f2fe9978a595867c0a7e7b9bd66bb","tid":26003,"uid":13771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201